text: Jia Yuping (born 3 May 1986) is a Chinese cross-country skier. She competed in the women's sprint at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of China Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
